    "note": "Design-first artifact only \u2014 describes the MCP tool surface, not a running server. Tool input/output schemas $ref the same object schemas as the OpenAPI; each tool maps to an OpenAPI operationId. Surfaces NYCHA's open reference data (developments, addresses, facilities, utility metering, resident statistics) and adds report_repair \u2014 the net-new write workflow locked today inside the Oracle Siebel Self Service Portal.",
